data.description: This is a one of a kind property that has been well maintained and well taken care of by current and only owners.  The location of this home is tucked away in a quaint court on a beautiful hillside overlooking the hills of north and east Vallejo. This home is a hidden gem you do not want to miss out on. As soon as you arrive to this home you will start to see all of the carefully sought out materials and details used to create this beautiful home oasis. Being close to Hans Park the home is surrounded by eucalyptus and redwood trees, with rear access to the park. Right off the main living room you can enjoy the views from the wrap around balcony facing north.    You can even relax in your own private master suite which includes a jetted bathtub.   The property surrounding the home is easy to maintain with a lawn area, rose garden and area for garden expansion as well as a back patio area great for entertaining.   The front of the property/driveway is paved and the entire home exterior/interior was built using almost all redwood.
